HEADWORD: Junco
<hw>Jun"co</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any
bird of the genus <gen>Junco</gen>, which includes several species of
North American finches; -- called also <altname>snowbird</altname>, or
<altname>blue snowbird</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

